<h3 id="par_idN1074C">Text to Table</h3>
<paragraph id="par_idN1074F" role="paragraph"><ahelp hid="." visibility="hidden">Opens a dialog where you can convert the selected text to a table.</ahelp> Opens <link href="text/swriter/01/06090000.xhp">a dialog</link> where you can convert the selected text to a table.</paragraph>
