<h3 id="par_idN10763">Table to Text</h3>
<paragraph id="par_idN10766" role="paragraph"><ahelp hid="." visibility="hidden">Opens a dialog where you can convert the current table to text.</ahelp> Opens <link href="text/swriter/01/06090000.xhp">a dialog</link> where you can convert the current table to text.</paragraph>

<h2 id="par_idN1092F">Edit Formula</h2>
